5.3 Professional education and lifelong learning

→ Xcelerate Your Potential at Siemens – XPS Leadership Program1 is an opportunity for outstanding candidates in the field of digital business management. By developing their skills and their global networks, the program sup- ports participants develop in leadership roles.

→ Finance Excellence Program (FEP) is a finance leadership program that builds a foundation for future commercial leaders with a digital mindset. Participants benefit from being assigned a personal mentor from Siemens’ finance leadership team and customized development measures.